		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />One solution that should give 16 bits' worth of entropy without having to time things faster than vblank: Require one press of Start to close the title screen and another to acknowledge the menu. Timing the press, release, press, and release, should end up with at least 7 good bits from the press, 2 from the release, 5 from the next press, and 2 from the release.

		

